premise_source_doc_sentence: The self-produced album is narrated by New York actor/director Michael Rapaport and features guest appearances from Talib Kweli , Posdnuos , Masta Ace , Kardinal Offishall , Styles P , Lil Fame , Gangrene , MC Eiht , King Tee , Celph Titled , Large Professor , Inspectah Deck , Rah Digga , Slaine , Ill Bill , Organized Konfusion , and The Doppelgangaz among others .
